    "attributes": {
        "action": "Criminal Record checks on drivers of taxis and private hire a legal requirement.",
        "additional_details": "Drivers of taxis and private hire vehicles are currently allowed to keep their licences and continue to work even if they have criminal convictions.",
        "background": "Currently no legal requirement only recommendations. There should be mandatory checks in place as a minimum requirement. Licences should be removed from those found to have violent or sexual convictions. We have a duty to protect women, children and the vulnerable and less able.",
